Stone Container Corp said it issplitting its common stock 2-for-1 and increasing its dividend33-1/3 pct.    The dividend of 20 cts a share, an increase of five ctsover the prior 15 cts a share on pre-split shares, is payableJune 12 to holders of record May 22.    The stock split also is payable June 12 to holders ofrecord May 22. Reuter&#3;